These are bitmap fonts to be used with thorn-to-gif and thorn-to-ppm. They are
human-readable and easy to modify. To use them with thorn-to-gif, do
    
    thorn | thorn-to-gif --font <fontname>

where <fontname> is a file in this directory. This font directory must be
in ~/.local/share/thorn/fonts to be visible.
